        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white p-3 rounded mb-3">
            <p>It's no surprise that finding a skilled planner can be challenging, as true supermen are rare. As Eugene once said, why should the Maintenance Planner waste their time acting as a "secretary" for various maintenance roles and departments, when their primary focus should be on plant health? It seems that individuals like mechanics, electricians, engineers, and accountants are content to let the planner handle everything, despite being handsomely compensated each month. If the beancounters take over, the outcome is predictable - just look at Enron and similar scandals.</p>
            <ul class="post-meta mb-0">
                <li class="post-date"><i class="uil uil-calendar-alt"></i><span>13-09-2024</span></li>
